TOPLEVEL DEZYNE README
**********************

BUILDING
========

Run:
    ./configure
    make

Try:
    make help

RUNNING
=======

Create fresh database and initialize 

    make database

Run dezyne server from the source tree

    webapp/server/main.js --debug --config=localhost

Run dezyne client from the source tree

    webapp/client/dzn

make sure to authenticate first

    echo test | webapp/client/dzn -u test -s http://localhost:3000 hello

INSTALLING
==========

Install client in $HOME:

    make client

PACKAGING AND DEPLOYMENT
========================

Run:
    make regression

Run:
    make dezyne-server
